parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Power Steering Failure due to Crankshaft Pulley Woodruff Key Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Woodruff key on the crankshaft pulley can cause the power steering system to malfunction, leading to a loss of steering control, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Sudden loss of power steering
steering wheel spinning freely
loss of steering control
engine stalling or shutting down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering belt can cause the power steering system to malfunction, leading to a loss of steering control, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Sudden loss of power steering
steering wheel spinning freely
loss of steering control.
